lead_paragraph: CUSHNY--Cora Cavanagh, passed peacefully at her home in Lexington, KY on May 26, 2016. She was born November 14, 1932, to James F. and Elise Burns Cavanaugh of Glen Head, NY. Funeral Service will be held at St. Paul's Catholic Church in Lexington, KY on Tuesday, May 31, 2016 at 10:00 am with a Memorial Service at 37 Frost Mill Road, Mill Neck, NY at 12:30 pm on June 18, 2016. In lieu of flowers, the family suggests donations to Hospice of the Bluegrass or the United States Equestrian Team. 1/3

headline.main: Paid Notice: Deaths  CUSHNY, CORA CAVANAGH
